txt.en: 'Hope you weren't slacking off on your patrol. I don't want to have to execute my favourite minion to make an example out someone who doesn't do their orders right!'
Shíktarb is at Shrak Mauruk.\n\nYou should listen to Shíktarb yell at you.
Shíktarb commands you to patrol the Eastern side of Osgiliath and make sure those pesky Men haven't crossed the river.
Patrol the bridge to the Dome of Stars
Patrol of overlook of the Northern courtyard
Patrol the Eastern side of Osgiliath.

'Those crafty Men have been spying on us! You better patrol the Eastern side of Osgiliath. Make sure they don't get the idea to come over here again.\n\n'If I see one, I sure won't be inviting him in for bones and slop! I'll kill him and eat him I will!'
Listen to Shíktarb yell at you
